\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid15282467 RP  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid11955618\charrsid5787272 Yes. Yes, I've been }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
